<button className="process-button" onClick={handleProcessCode}>
          Process Code
        </button>
        {['Original', 'Decomposed'].map((tab) => (
          <button
            key={tab}
            onClick={() => setActiveTab(tab)}
            style={{
              padding: '10px',
              margin: '0 5px',
              backgroundColor: activeTab === tab ? '#007BFF' : '#ccc',
              color: '#fff',
              border: 'none',
              borderRadius: '5px',
              cursor: 'pointer',
            }}
          >
            {tab}
          </button>
        ))}
